==KanColle Style 3(艦これスタイル 参)==
[[File:KanColle Style 3.jpg|right|thumb|120px]]
This mook covers material regarding the browser game up to the [[Fall 2016 Event]] and covers the editors' viewpoints and strategies they used to conquer the event. In addition, there is a section dedicated showing off various Kancolle related events and dining locations such as Irako's Canteen / PX, the [[Naval District Saury Festival in Yokohama]] and bar table counter information. The mook also features an in depth look at the KanColle Arcade and the Movie. Finally there are interviews featuring [[Kensuke Tanaka]], [[Tanibe Yumi Interview: Kancolle Style Vol. 3|Yumi Tanibe]] and [[Akasaki Chinatsu]].

Mook features the Shiratsuyu-Class Destroyers: [[Shiratsuyu]], [[Murasame]] [[Shigure]] and [[Yuudachi]].

